description: The Testudo Melody shares some similarities with the Ryokka TU-77a salvage pod, but with batteries, canisters, intake regulators and RCS thrusters all on the outside. It's a more capable ship than the ubiquitous Ryokka model, but more difficult to maintain, especially without an EVA suit.
